<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Matthew Hyeun]]></title><description><![CDATA[Matthew Hyeun]]></description><link>https://lumen.netlify.com</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Thu, 19 Nov 2020 02:53:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[Victory for Democracy in Bolivia]]></title><description><![CDATA[Luis Arce of the Movement for Socialism (MAS) party will be inaugurated as the next President of Bolivia on November 8th, 2020 after a landslide victory in the 2020 general election. Following a long year of violent political unrest caused by a U.S-backed coup, not only is this a convincing victory for the MAS, but also for democracy as a whole.]]></description><link>https://lumen.netlify.com/posts/victory-for-democracy-in-bolivia</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://lumen.netlify.com/posts/victory-for-democracy-in-bolivia</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Nov 2020 02:49:21 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
